📌 Practice Problem: Sum of Two Integers
Take two integer variables `a` and `b` with constant values and print their sum.
Example-
Input- a = 5
       b = 7

Solution

public class SumOfTwoIntegers {
    public static void main(String[] args) {

        int a = 5;
        int b = 7;

        System.out.println(a + b);
    }
}
  
Output- 12
Time Complexity
O(1)
Space Complexity
O(1)
